# Better Auth Documentation

Use current Better Auth docs — do not rely on training data for API details.

## Priority 1: Context7 MCP

Use Context7 `query-docs` with library ID `/better-auth/better-auth`.

Example queries:

- "email OTP plugin sendVerificationOTP disableSignUp"
- "magic link plugin sendMagicLink"
- "crossSubDomainCookies trustedOrigins baseURL"
- "drizzle adapter schema plugins"
- "createAuthClient emailOTPClient Hono integration"

Workflow: search with the user's specific auth feature, then confirm API shape before implementing.

## Priority 2: Direct sources (shell fallback)

```bash
# Doc index
curl -s https://www.better-auth.com/llms.txt

# Fetch a page as Markdown (Accept header)
curl -sH "Accept: text/markdown" https://www.better-auth.com/docs/plugins/email-otp
curl -sH "Accept: text/markdown" https://www.better-auth.com/docs/integrations/hono
curl -sH "Accept: text/markdown" https://www.better-auth.com/docs/concepts/cookies
curl -sH "Accept: text/markdown" https://www.better-auth.com/docs/reference/options
```

GitHub source (when docs page is unclear):

```bash
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/better-auth/better-auth/main/docs/content/docs/plugins/email-otp.mdx
```

Official docs: https://www.better-auth.com/docs

## Conventions in this repo

- Auth runs on the **API worker** only (`apps/api/src/auth/`).
- HTTP routes: `/api/auth/*` on Hono; frontend proxies same-origin `/api/auth/*`.
- Browser auth client: `apps/frontend/src/lib/auth-client.ts` — `baseURL` is `VITE_API_URL`.
- Database: Drizzle adapter with `authSchema` in `apps/api/src/schema/`.
- Sign-in method: **Email OTP** (`emailOTP` plugin) — no passwords, `disableSignUp: true`.
- Allowed users: validate email against `ALLOWED_USERS` before sending OTP.
- Dev: log OTP to API console; production: send via Resend + React Email.

## Plugin quick reference

| Plugin | Server import | Client import |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Email OTP | `emailOTP` from `better-auth/plugins` | `emailOTPClient` from `better-auth/client/plugins` |
| Magic link | `magicLink` from `better-auth/plugins` | `magicLinkClient` from `better-auth/client/plugins` |

## Notes

- Better Auth ships an official remote docs MCP — see https://www.better-auth.com/docs/ai/mcp if configured in the dashboard.
- `@better-auth/cli` generates/migrates auth schema — run from `apps/api` when plugin schema changes.
- Do not await email sending inside `sendVerificationOTP` if timing attacks are a concern; in Workers use `waitUntil` for background send (see Better Auth email OTP docs).
